node.text: Love it! Being Healthy is Wholistic. Moderate Caffine, Embrace Yoga and Balanced Diet!

We will be exiting the #CircuitBreaker in a few days' time into Phase One 🥳🎊🎉, which is Safe Re-Opening. Hurray! ❤

However, under that phase, restaurant dine-ins are still not allowed, which means that it will be some time before the F&B industry can thrive once more. 🍽  Which is all the more why we need to support our #localfnb to ensure that they are still standing in the post-Covid era. 😘😘😘 We've put up a list of 10 local F&B brands that you can support and keep alive during this crucial period. Visit the link in our Bio! 😊

#supportfnbsg #savefnbsg
@pampingparty Yahhhh, definitely can't wait for dine-ins to be allowed once more!!! 😍😍😍
Despite being able to dabao, just sitting at a cafe feels so nice and we miss it. Stay safe!
Love it! Being Healthy is Wholistic. Moderate Caffine, Embrace Yoga and Balanced Diet!
